title: Black Inc Five 5-spoke carbon road wheels promise speed, distinctive looks
content:
Factor bike’s Black Inc component brand has launched the FIVE, a lightweight 5-spoke carbon road bike wheelset developed to make you go fast and stand out from the crowd while doing so.
